Title: Demons
Consuming Amazon AWS Notifications using MassTransit
Description:
Amazon Web Services (AWS) uses its Simple Notification Service (SNS) extensively to route all types of events. In this video, I cover a new sample that shows how to consume SNS events using MassTransit and Amazon SQS. The Simple Email Service (SES) sends bounce and complaint notifications via SNS, and this sample consumes those notifications so that they can be handled by your application domain.
